item.title: CVE-2023-42132|2023-10-02T04:12:32.133Z -- ministry%20of%20health%2C%20labour%20and%20welfare -- fd%20application
item.description: FD Application Apr. 2022 Edition (Version 9.01) and earlier improperly restricts XML external entity references (XXE). By processing a specially crafted XML file, arbitrary files on the system may be read by an attacker.
